{"_id":"tZo8QZBZrH9fBeNI","name":"Betrayed Phantom","type":"class","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/tokens/betrayed-phantom.png","data":{"abilities":"<p>Touched by the grave, 3d6+2 Presence. Cold, 3d6-2 Toughness.</p>\n<p>Can choose to pass through one of the following: Wood, natural stone, flesh.</p>\n<p>Roll d6 on the Weapons table and d2 on the Armor table.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Begin with one of the following:</p>\n<p>1. Keepsake Coin. Placed on your corpse's eyes by some kind soul. You always know the location of the wraith wearing your skin.</p>\n<p>2. Deathmask. The funeral mask you were meant to wear. When donned, reduce the DR of all social rolls when communing with any undead.</p>\n<p>3. Prayer Book. Your mother wanted you to have it. You start with a Sacred Scroll.</p>\n<p>4. Finger Bone. Possibly belonged to a priest. No crypt, tomb, cemetery gate or catacomb can lock you out. 5. Tragic Letter. You must deliver it to someone. Only then can you be reunited with your body.</p>\n<p>6. Glass Eye. Not yours. Place it in your skull to see through any illusion.</p>","armorTableDie":"1d2","description":"YOU DIED. Fallen on the battlefield, your soul began to rot. Between earth and the beyond, SOMETHING REACHED OUT. You \ntook its bargain, and it took your body. \nNOW YOU ARE A SHADE, alive again but half-existent. Your  second chance at life is denied you, and a wraith now wears your skin.","omenDie":"1d4","startingAgility":"3d6","startingHitPoints":"1d6","startingItems":"morkborg-3p.class-betrayed-phantom,Touched by the Grave","startingPresence":"3d6+2","startingRolls":"morkborg-3p.rolls-betrayed-phantom,Betrayed Phantom Items,1\nmorkborg-3p.rolls-betrayed-phantom,Betrayed Phantom Origins","startingSilver":"0","startingStrength":"3d6","startingToughness":"3d6-2","weaponTableDie":"1d6"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"EI4zbOlxQspAyGze":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.HJU9wkPjNsRcavL1"}}}
